I really believe that the British person who is doing the videos on You-Tube is really doing a disservice to what evp research is all about. Kind of like the Ouija board, I am sure that a lot of people will want to get a hacked radio as a result of these videos for the wrong reason. I found a video on You-Tube of the person who sent the radio to this Jamie guy his name is Vinnie he has several videos himself on his boxes.

  I am glad I found this group to get started in researching evps. I havent started doing any recorded sessions myself. I am still learning from all the wonderful people on this site. 

  Thanks 

  Kay


